title: Crime Locations for Drug Offenses, Salt Lake City, Utah, 2.2010
name: Crime Locations for Drug Offenses, Salt Lake City, Utah, 2.2010
description:
This dataset displays lat/lon locations of the locations where drug offenses occurred during the month of February 2010 (2.4.2010 - 3.4.2010)

The data was received from crimereports.com. A time query was set for the past thirty days in the area around downtown Salt Lake City. The addresses were then geocoded to obtain the lat/lon locations of the offense locations.
